        <title type="html"><![CDATA[食用Gridea5分创建免费github博客]]></title>
        <id>https://kukudexiaoxiaomaya.github.io/post/shi-yong-gridea5-fen-chuang-jian-mian-fei-github-bo-ke/</id>
        <link href="https://kukudexiaoxiaomaya.github.io/post/shi-yong-gridea5-fen-chuang-jian-mian-fei-github-bo-ke/">
        </link>
        <updated>2020-04-13T06:47:07.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>下载Gridea https://gridea.dev/<br>
运行Gridea<br>
创建仓库<br>
启动 github page<br>
在配置页面按github情况填写即可<br>
点击保存<br>
点击同步<br>
访问XXXXX.github.io即可</p>
]]></content>
